thread.title: Jenny Zhao

author: Jenny Zhao
title: Jenny Zhao
text: I hired All Pro Floors through homeadvisor, and hired it to install new engineered hardwood floors. They are very knowledgeable, pay great attention to details and did cleaning every day before leaving. The owner and contractor Rustin tries everything to meet all my requests and provided a beautiful wood floor products. I am very happy with the work done.
